stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> SessionWaitingForUser

  SessionWaitingForUser --> CoreStreaming: send SubmitInput to minimal loop

  CoreStreaming --> SessionWaitingForUser: minimal loop emits FinalAssistantResponse
  CoreStreaming --> CoreStreamingFailed: host observes model stream error
  CoreStreaming --> RunningAutoApprovedTools: minimal loop emits ModelToolCallBatchReady + all calls auto-approved
  CoreStreaming --> PendingUserAction: minimal loop emits ModelToolCallBatchReady + at least one call requires user intervention
  CoreStreaming --> SessionWaitingForUser: minimal loop handles LLM-turn Interrupt

  CoreStreamingFailed --> CoreStreaming: user retries response
  CoreStreamingFailed --> CoreStreaming: user chats, send SubmitInput to minimal loop

  RunningAutoApprovedTools --> CoreStreaming: auto-approved calls done, send SubmitHostFeedback to minimal loop
  RunningAutoApprovedTools --> SessionWaitingForUser: minimal loop handles tool-call-state Interrupt

  PendingUserAction --> PendingUserAction: user approves/denies/cancels one tool call
  PendingUserAction --> RunningUserApprovedTools: all calls resolved + approved calls exist
  PendingUserAction --> CoreStreaming: all calls resolved + no approved calls, send SubmitHostFeedback to minimal loop
  PendingUserAction --> SessionWaitingForUser: minimal loop handles tool-call-state Interrupt

  RunningUserApprovedTools --> CoreStreaming: approved calls done, send SubmitHostFeedback to minimal loop
  RunningUserApprovedTools --> SessionWaitingForUser: minimal loop handles tool-call-state Interrupt
